title: Euro 2016 Qualifier: Goal machine Lewandowski secures Poland's ticket to France
text: Robert Lewandowski scored the winner to secure Poland a place at Euro 2016 with a 2-1 victory in Warsaw on Sunday that consigned a battling Ireland side to the playoffs. Lewandowski's header just before halftime in the Group D match was his 15th goal in the last six games for his club Bayern Munich and country Â»
